---
const steps = [
  { title: 'Customer reaches out for a quote', subtext: 'call, text, or form' },
  { title: 'Their request is captured and logged', subtext: 'nothing gets missed' },
  { title: 'They receive a follow-up', subtext: 'automatic or manual' },
  { title: 'Everything is organized in one place', subtext: 'no confusion, no duplication' },
  { title: 'The job is scheduled or quoted', subtext: 'clear next step' }
];
---

<section class="py-24 bg-charcoal-800">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white text-center mb-4">
      Here's what should happen when someone contacts your business:
    </h2>

    <!-- Subtext -->
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Right now, things probably slip through the cracks — messages get missed, follow-ups don't happen, and work becomes inconsistent.
    </p>

    <!-- Vertical Workflow -->
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
      {steps.map((step, index) => (
        <>
          <div class="w-full max-w-md">
            <div class="bg-charcoal-700 border border-charcoal-500 rounded-lg px-6 py-5 shadow-lg shadow-charcoal-900/50">
              <p class="text-white font-medium mb-1">{step.title}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">{step.subtext}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          {index < steps.length - 1 && (
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center py-3">
              <div class="w-0.5 h-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-charcoal-500 to-charcoal-400"></div>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-charcoal-400 -mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          )}
        </>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Explanation -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-3">
        We don't replace your business or rebuild everything from scratch
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10">
        We work with the systems and processes already in place — helping keep things organized and consistent.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-3">
        Your team already does the work
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        We support how things are handled so nothing gets missed and everything continues moving forward.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
